1913年秋，[[清华学校|清华学校]]聘请了新的美籍音乐教师 Miss Katharine Elizabeth Seelye<ref name=汪端伟>{{Cite web|url=https://xsg.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8351/2018/20180904155800207825664/20180904155800207825664_.html |title=清华大学校歌的前世与今生|accessdate=2020-04-06|author=汪端伟 |date=2018-09-04 |work= |publisher=清华大学校史研究室 |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405165114/https://xsg.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8351/2018/20180904155800207825664/20180904155800207825664_.html|archivedate=2020-04-05|deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | author = 苏云峰 | title = 近代中國高等教育硏究 | location =  | publisher = Zhong yang yan jiu yuan jin dai shi yan jiu suo | date = 2008-05-19 | pages = 143 | ISBN = 9576714583 | accessdate = 2019-09-15 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=542aAAAAIAAJ&q=Miss+Katharine+Elizabeth+Seelye+%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF&dq=Miss+Katharine+Elizabeth+Seelye+%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwji48L7pdLkAhXiNKYKHWkiDYQQ6AEIKDAA | language = zh | quote =  | archive-date = 2020-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200209001313/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=542aAAAAIAAJ&q=Miss+Katharine+Elizabeth+Seelye+%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF&dq=Miss+Katharine+Elizabeth+Seelye+%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwji48L7pdLkAhXiNKYKHWkiDYQQ6AEIKDAA | dead-url = no }}</ref>，她为清华学校撰写了[[英文|英文]]校歌。歌词刊登在1914年的《清華年刊》<ref>{{Cite book | author = Miss Katharine Elizabeth Seelye | title = The Tsing Hua Annual | location = 北京 | publisher = 普林斯頓大學 | year = 1914 | pages = 40 | ISBN =  | accessdate = 2020-04-06 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?hl=zh-TW&id=UYpPAAAAYAAJ&dq=cheer+for+old+tsing+hua&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=come+and+join+our+hearty+song | language = en | archive-date = 2020-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200407031046/https://books.google.com.tw/books?hl=zh-TW&id=UYpPAAAAYAAJ&dq=cheer+for+old+tsing+hua&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=come+and+join+our+hearty+song | dead-url = no }}</ref>，词曲刊登在1916年的《清華年刊》<ref name=汪端伟/>。「Tsing Hua College Song」的歌曲词谱，內容符合清華幹練、團結的作風，完全的美式风格<ref name="清華研讀間">{{Cite web|url=https://www.iread.one/2201067.html |title=揭秘-清華校歌背後的故事 |accessdate=2017-11-02 |author=小屈  付琳  王鵬飛 李澤翰 |date=2017-09-05 |publisher=清华研讀間 |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102125500/https://www.iread.one/2201067.html |archivedate=2017-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

類似地，同时期還产生了拉拉队歌《清华优胜歌》（Tsing Hua Song 或 Cheer for Old Tsing Hua）<ref>{{Cite book | author =陳惠發 | title = 我的生涯與省思 | location =  | publisher = Global Publishing |date= 2009-11-01 | pages = 366|ISBN =9813205563| accessdate =2020-04-06  | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=RSNYDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA366&dq=%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E5%95%A6%E5%95%A6%E9%9A%8ATSinghua+Fight+Song&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiSxbavs9LoAhWSBKYKHZdzDkoQ6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=Fight%20Song&f=false| language= zh-cn  }}</ref>。刊載於1914年8月《清华年刊》上<ref>{{Cite book | author = Miss Katharine Elizabeth Seelye | title = The Tsing Hua Annual| location = 北京 | publisher = 普林斯頓大學 |year= 1914 | pages = 50|ISBN =| accessdate =2020-04-06  | url =https://books.google.com.tw/books?hl=zh-TW&id=UYpPAAAAYAAJ&dq=cheer+for+old+tsing+hua&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=Cheer+for+old+Tsing+Hua| language= en  }}</ref>，没有明确表明作者，其采用「Amherst Fight Song」乐谱，歌词亦與之相近<ref name="初沐美风，继承儒典" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amherstfootball.com/comet-pride.html |title=CHEER FOR OLD AMHERST |access-date=2018-05-19 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119091553/https://www.amherstfootball.com/comet-pride.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，深受學生欢迎，常在校队比赛时齐唱<ref name="新竹清华大学：校歌的由来"/>。

前二首校歌於1917年通过征文，被译为中文，刊登在同年6月的《清华周刊·增刊》上<ref name="初沐美风，继承儒典">{{Cite web|url=http://www.tsinghua.org.cn/publish/alumni/4000382/10049367.html |title=关于清华校歌——初沐美风，继承儒典 |accessdate=2010-11-01 |author=孟凡茂 |date=2010-08-27 |work=清華校友總會 |publisher=清华大学校史研究室 |language=zh |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923211726/http://www.tsinghua.org.cn/publish/alumni/4000382/10049367.html |archivedate=2016-09-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="新竹清华大学：校歌的由来">{{Cite web|url=http://archives.lib.nthu.edu.tw/history/emblem/emblem06.html |title=校歌的由來 |accessdate=2010-11-01 |author=国立清华大学图书馆 |work=國立清華大學數位校史館 |publisher=國立清華大學 |language=zh |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916064941/http://archives.lib.nthu.edu.tw/history/emblem/emblem06.html |archivedate=2016-09-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
